sub_title: Bachelors in Biological Sciences, Pursuing a Masters in Science and Business Management. Seeking an internship in Business Development, Project Management and Marketing
summary: I began with the study of biology and chemistry, and during this time I learned a lot of skills exclusive to the field, being analytical, planning and managing projects along with a research team, facilitation, solving problems, developing presentation and public speaking skills, researching, communications and more. Now I'm moving to the business field by continuing my studies at Utrecht University in the Science and Business Management MBA. I have a broad background and wide range of extracurricular activities. Looking for my first opportunity to break into the business world.
